# AutoReqGen
âš¡ A smarter alternative to pipreqs â€” AutoReqGen scans your entire project recursively, accurately generates requirements.txt with exact versions, formats your code using tools like Black or isort, and even auto-generates documentation from your docstrings. One tool to automate and optimize your Python workflow.
